alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.simulator
Class Tag

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.simulator.Tag
public class Tag
extends java.lang.Object

The Tag class is a collection of static strings that are the names of various properties and events that are used throughout the simulation. These names appear in the properties file that is input to the simulation, in the output log file, or, sometimes, both.
